title.narrative: Sustainable Development in Poor Rural Areas

description.narrative: The project's development objective is to explore and pilot more effective and innovative ways of providing poverty reduction assistance to the poorest communities and households in Henan Province, Shaanxi Province and Chongqing Municipality (the Project Provinces) through community driven development and participatory approaches.

condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 paragraph 3(a) of the GEF Grant Agreement | Description :Within 3 months after effectiveness or laterdate the Bank may agree, the recipient will provide a simplified version of the SLMA Manual in Chinese to cover village assessmentimplementation etc. | Due Date :16-Feb-2011

Finance Agreement :Section 1 (B) of Schedule 2 of Loan Agreement | Description :Maintain throughout the implementation of theProject the Central Project Coordination Office (CPCO) with powers, functions, staffand resources, satisfactory to the Bank. |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Section 1 paragraph 1 of Schedule of the Project Agreement | Description :Each Project Implementing Entitieswill maintain a provincial PPLG/PPMO, a municipal MPLG/MPMO, a county CPLG/CPMO, Township Stations, village committees, and naturalvillage project groups. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Section 1 paragraph 2 of Schedule of Project Agreement | Description :Furnish to the Bank for review not laterthan November 15 in each calendar year an annual work program for activities proposed to be implemented during the followingcalendar year. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Section 1 paragraph 3 of Schedule of Project Agreement | Description :Project Implementing Entities will applyand cause the Project counties and villages to apply, in the project implementation, the CDD, CDF and SLMA all satisfactory to theBank. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Section II (A) of Schedule 2 of the Loan Agreement | Description :Furnish project reports, covering the periodof one calendar semester, not later than three months after the end of the period covered by such report. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Section II (B) of Schedule 2 of the Loan Agreement | Description :As part of the Progress Report, provide notlater than 90 days after the end of each calendar semester, interim unaudited financialreports. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Section II (B) of Schedule 2 of the Loan Agreement | Description :Provide audited Financial Statements for eachsuch period to the Bank not later than six months after the end of such period. | Frequency :Yearly
